UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=5407; /* Text0_1: All requests for my work must be made in person by the buyer. Orwin often asks me to reconsider, but my priorities lie here. Look around you: many of these fighters rely upon me for their armor. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=5408; /* Text0_1: I only wish I had more students like you. Not many will venture so far into enemy territory. I salute your courage. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=5409; /* Text0_1: We cannot afford to give an inch in this war. Day and night, I create new armor, and I patch whatever can be salvaged from the old. I have no time for other tasks. Would you take care of something for me? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=5410; /* Text0_1: You have wasted your time and mine by coming to me for training, $N. I have no time to teach basic skills. We\'re fighting a war here, and this is one of the front lines. Don\'t return to me until you are more prepared. */
