UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=7872; /* Text0_1: Welcome to the Falconwing Square Inn. May I prepare a meal for you, or ready a room? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=7874; /* Text0_1: Hail, $c.  The Ironforge Brigade is stationed here to keep an eye on Hive\'Zora.  The Cenarion Circle druids have been monitoring silithid movement and they\'re anticipating something major in this area. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=7875; /* Text0_1: The Captain is busy at the moment.  He\'s studying maps we recently acquired of the underground silithid hives.  Stay with us if you\'d like to help, he\'ll come out any moment now. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=7876; /* Text0_1: Hey mon, you be here ta bring me mithril bars no doubt. There be big trouble brewin\' in the Silithus desert at Ahn\'Qiraj. We and the Alliance goin\' all out this time to stop them bugs, and that be why you seein\' everyone here.$B$BThe Horde be askin\' me to collect $2009w for the war effort, but I only have $2008w. So ya gonna help me out, or what? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=7878; /* Text0_1: Hello, young $c. Are you here to bring me a batch of peacebloom? We are collecting them to make potions and elixirs for the Ahn\'Qiraj war effort. Though tragic that we are forced into this war, the results will be even more terrible if we do not prepare properly.$B$BThe Horde has tasked me with the collection of $2020w peacebloom, and so far we\'ve managed to put together $2021w. If you have it within your ability, please gather up all that you can and return them to me here. */
