UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=7962; /* Text0_1: Hello, $c. From what I\'ve been told, everything\'s been collected, and all of the materiel for the war is being shipped over to Silithus as we speak. It should all be there in less than $2113w days. Once that\'s done, and the gong has been rung with the Scepter of the Shifting Sands, the war will really begin. */
