UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=8466; /* Text0_1: If it is a matter of import that you wish to speak on, $c, it may be more appropriate to seek an audience with Dame Auriferous. I warn you though, she is very busy and you may be in for quite a wait. */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=8467; /* Text0_1: Normally it would not be my place to speak with you directly; rather, you would seek an audience with milady. However, I did give you a task directly, so what is it that we need to discuss? */
UPDATE locales_npc_text SET  WHERE entry=8468; /* Text0_1: $C, Dame Auriferous has conveyed to me her great pleasure in the service that you have done us in the past. She wishes to extend to you her hope that you will continue to be a champion of sin\'dorei interests here in the Ghostlands. */
